title: TOOTTMM - Wear watch face
summary: TOOTTMM - designer watch face app for Android Wear
description: Eyes on time. Two faces and two lines. The left one shows the hours, the right shows five minutes to spare. TOOTTMM has a nine colors customization and works in ambient mode. Watch your time.Compatible with Huawei Watch, Motorola Moto 360, LG G Watch, LG G Watch R, Samsung Gear Live, Asus ZenWatch, Sony SmartWatch 3Idea & design : Albert SalamonAndroid programming : Michał Żyliński© 2015 COPYRIGHT Albert Salamon
descriptionHTML:
Eyes on time. Two faces and two lines. The left one shows the hours, the right shows five minutes to spare. TOOTTMM has a nine colors customization and works in ambient mode. Watch your time.

Compatible with Huawei Watch, Motorola Moto 360, LG G Watch, LG G Watch R, Samsung Gear Live, Asus ZenWatch, Sony SmartWatch 3

Idea & design : Albert Salamon
Android programming : Michał Żyliński
